                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d375">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 322.112St8/3.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Hartman</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Quito</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-05-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 22, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s May 14. I presented case of Strong this afternoon and at seven
                    o’clock the Minister for Foreign Affairs informed me that orders had been
                    telegraphed to Manta for his release. Full report by mail.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hartman</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
